::DarkMouse::

She looked at Scorponok. A program surge went through her mind. She 
whispered,"We are on duty. We must obey Megatron first." She tried to smile 
but couldn't.  She wanted to hug Scorponok, but her programming wouldn't 
allow it. While Megatron was near, she could only obey him. Megatron was 
first to be obeyed.  Quickstrike second and Scorponok third according to her 
new programming.  She stayed cold and showed no emotion while Megatron was 
near her.
She watched Megatron while he talked to Panzertron.
